Global Fuel Data

Task

Write down a question or hypothesis you are interested in exploring from the world powerplant dataset found in the information is beautiful website, which includes some nice visualizations. The original data can be found here along with a brief description. You might want to work with just a subset of the data (e.g. one particular country), or you may choose to transform or summarize your data in the way that best allows you to explore your question.

Question or Hypothesis

How did Gas and Hydro power generated in the United States of America differ from 2013 to 2017?
